{"tid":2282014,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"要求立法禁止毒撚喺感情台叫春","createTime":"2020-11-11T13:54:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T13:59:59.000Z","uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5b8518fa57b4d0e63857f237cfd281e47e891deb","tid":2282014,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T13:54:57.000Z","msg":"每次見親啲毒撚開po就想像到佢地流晒口水覆人個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頭先食緊飯 睇到個毒撚開po差啲嘔咗出嚟<br />\n好心你地咪撚叫春啦 隔住個mon都聽到你地未發育變緊聲果把毒撚聲<br />\n屌你老母全部毒撚個係樣衰人賤性格閪 仲要臭撚到仆街<br />\n我代表藍波撚要求立法禁止毒撚喺感情台叫春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLunch哥見字可摸以幫我寫信比林奠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支持:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主好波:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樣衰唔係罪，係不幸。生得醜唔係你嘅責任，要怪嘅，只好怪上帝<br />\n但係，毒，就係你嘅錯！ 一個人好地地係唔會毒嘅，你變得做毒撚，梗係心理精神都有問題啦 喺呢個人人都用交友app嘅時代，你竟然唔撚識社交？ 毒係冇用嘅表現，係廢柴嘅象徵 毒撚畸形扭曲嘅性格，已經充分顯示出佢哋嘅唔道德<br />\n毒撚係罪犯，佢哋甚至比小偷、殺人犯更無恥 一般犯人都會掩飾自己犯咗嘅罪 但係毒撚，佢哋竟然將自己嘅罪證透過氣場同臭味發放，就好似一個殺人犯拖住條屍周街走咁 你話，見到毒撚有乜辦法唔憤怒？<br />\n所以，見到毒撚應該即刻鬧佢，就算唔鬧佢都要鄙視佢，我哋要透過侮辱嚟喚醒佢嘅良知 喺街見到毒撚唔鬧佢，就好似搭地鐵見到肥婆一人坐兩個位唔出聲一樣 作為一個有良知嘅人，我哋應該出聲，應該鼓起勇氣挺身而出鬧到佢哋狗血淋頭！"},{"pid":"9cab9761e390d652ec15dc0befc80c4e62f0a4bd","tid":2282014,"uid":374184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T13:55:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b78016ce1431a6bf56a2375454b8c3576a40c70","tid":2282014,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"9cab9761e390d652ec15dc0befc80c4e62f0a4bd","tid":2282014,"uid":374184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T13:55:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T13:55:44.000Z","msg":"咪能踢爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0897fd6bb7bd679902db05efafc0b22bad531849","tid":2282014,"uid":374184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T13:56:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e0d051f777f583110a6298219a1bd9722712d230","tid":2282014,"uid":2590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T13:59:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}